description:
Where Leaders Talk

Radio TI is a project created by the participants of the Advanced Future Leaders Program and is an initiative of the Toastmasters Leadership Institute of Toastmasters International District 74. The program was lead by Frank Tsuro, A past District Director of Southern Africa.

Radio TI serves as a host channel for various programs in which each participant produces their own content.
